OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773144183
OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe war in Iran could hit "every
OL,8,Fhousehold and every business" in the
OL,9,FUK, the prime minister has warned, as
OL,10,Fhe promised "to get ahead" of any
OL,11,Fpotential impact on people's finances.
OL,13,FSpeaking at a community centre in
OL,14,FLondon after the price of oil surged
OL,15,Fto a four-year high, the prime
OL,16,Fminister said: "The longer this goes
OL,17,Fon, the more likely the potential for
OL,18,Fan impact on our economy, impact on
OL,19,Fthe lives and households of everybody
OL,20,Fand every business."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
