FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773144183
OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe PM said the government's job is to
OL,8,F"get ahead of that, to look round the
OL,9,Fcorner, assess the risk."
OL,11,FHe insisted the economy is better
OL,12,Fplace to absorb the impact of war in
OL,13,Fcomparison to the Ukraine invasion in
OL,14,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
