OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773144183
OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FStarmer said: "I do understand the
OL,8,Fanxiety now, at nine days into this
OL,9,Fconflict, where a number of people
OL,10,Fwill be saying, 'well, now is the
OL,11,Fsituation going to get worse, and
OL,12,Fhow's it going to impact me and my
OL,13,Ffamily?'
OL,15,F"At the moment, what we're doing is
OL,16,Fmonitoring the risk, working with
OL,17,Fothers to mitigate the risk.
OL,19,FOil prices have soared above $100 a
OL,20,Fbarrel for the first time since 2022
OL,21,Fin response to the crisis.
