OL,7,FLondon's FTSE 100 Index fell nearly 2%
OL,8,Fsoon after opening as the Middle East
OL,9,Fconflict caused an acute supply crunch.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FMost UK households will be protected
OL,17,Ffrom the impact of rising energy
OL,18,Fprices in the short-term by the energy
OL,19,Fprice cap. But rising oil prices will
OL,20,Fbe felt by consumers at the pump.
