OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe Bank of England is now unlikely to
OL,8,Fcut interest rates this month,
OL,9,Fcontrary to earlier expectations, as
OL,10,Frising energy costs have increased the
OL,11,Frisk of higher inflation.
OL,13,FFinance ministers from the G7 group of
OL,14,Fleading democracies, including
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, will meet
OL,16,Fvirtually on Monday to discuss the
OL,17,Fcrisis.
