OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FStarmer said the US and the UK "are
OL,8,Fworking together every single day, as
OL,9,Fthey always have" despite the public
OL,10,Fattacks on him by Trump.
OL,12,F"I had a telephone call with President
OL,13,FTrump yesterday talking about the
OL,14,Fconflict in Iran and the region and
OL,15,Fwhat we were doing together, and that
OL,16,Fwas important in terms of the ongoing
OL,17,Fdiscussion," he said.
