OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FBut he added that "decisions about
OL,8,Fwhat's in Britain's best interests are
OL,9,Fdecisions for the Prime Minister of
OL,10,FBritain, and that's how I've
OL,11,Fapproached all of the questions and
OL,12,Fall the decisions that I've had to
OL,13,Fmake".
OL,15,FEarlier this week, the president said
OL,16,Fhe was "not happy" with Starmer over
OL,17,Fhis decision not to get involved in
OL,18,Fthe initial strikes.
