OL,3,CIran war could hit 'every household
OL,4,Cand every business' in UK, Starmer
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FHe also said, "This is not Winston
OL,8,FChurchill that we're dealing with",
OL,9,Fafter Starmer denied him permission to
OL,10,Flaunch strikes on Iran from UK
OL,11,Fterritory.
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump has sought
OL,14,Fto play down the impact of the turmoil
OL,15,Funleashed by joint US-Israeli attacks
OL,16,Fon Iran on February 28, insisting the
OL,17,Fprices will "drop rapidly when the
OL,18,Fdestruction of the Iran nuclear threat
OL,19,Fis over" and were a "very small price
OL,20,Fto pay".
